proprety of css: 
position 
values: 
static, abslout, relative, fixed- abslout and relative are similar 

static: default nothing changed. 
fixed: like the red bar in the frub hub will always be there. 
relative:  it doesn't move- unless if you put -50 px bottom for example.  
abslout: will not preserve original position of an element. will not overlap. 

